dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon data layer represents land use for Trempealeau County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Trempealeau_LandUse_2017.gdb.
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [Future Land Use for the County]

This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
